<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 71. Genus Larnaca: A–C, L. nigricornis sp. nov. male holotype (A–B) and paratype (C); D–G, L. eugenii (Griffini, 1914) male holotype (D–E) and male from Tay Yen Tu (F–G); H–I, L. tenuis sp. nov. female holotype; J–K, L. samkos sp. nov. female holotype; L–N, L. subaptera sp. nov. male holotype; O–P, L. squamiptera sp. nov. female holotype; Q, L. larnacoides (Karny, 1937) female in Karny collection (not a type).—Habitus dorsal view (A, D, F, H, K, L, O), do. lateral view (M, Q), face (B–C, E, G, I–J, N, P).—Scales 10 mm (habitus), 5 mm (face), not all images to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109160>
    dc:description "FIGURE 72. Genus Larnaca: A–D, L. nigricornis sp. nov. male holotype (A–B) and paratype (C–D); E–H, L. eugenii (Griffini, 1914) holotype (E) and male from Tay Yen Tu (F–H); I–L, L. subaptera sp. nov. holotype.—Male abdominal apex in dorso-apical and apical view (A–G, I), ventral view (H, K) and oblique lateral view (J), stridulatory pegs on second and third abdominal tergites, front is right (L)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109218>
    dc:description "FIGURE 101. A, Capnogryllacris (C.) sakaerat toxica ssp. nov. female paratype; B, Furcilarnaca salit sp. nov. male holotype; C, Ultragryllacris triangula sp. nov. male; D, Ultragryllacris pulchra nan ssp. nov. male holotype; E, Larnaca (L.) nigricornis sp. nov. female; F, Ocellarnaca angulata Gorochov, 2004 female; G, Larnaca (Larnaca) squamiptera sp. nov. female holotype; H, Siamgryllacris rufa sp. nov. female. Photos E–F by Jérome Constant." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109218/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

